N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 108.9 - Inspection of processing operations

State Regulations

The certifying agency shall make as many inspections of
both the seed and records as may be required to satisfy itself that only the
seed meeting requirements is labeled with certification tags. Notes
